# PWA Icons Required

The PWA needs these icons in the `public/` folder:
- icon-192.png (192x192px)
- icon-512.png (512x512px)

## Quick Fix Options:

### Option 1: Use existing logo
If you have a logo.png or similar:
```bash
cp public/logo.png public/icon-192.png
cp public/logo.png public/icon-512.png
```

### Option 2: Generate from existing image
Use an image resizer or:
- Visit https://realfavicongenerator.net/
- Upload your logo
- Generate PWA icons

### Option 3: Simple colored square (temporary)
Create simple colored squares as placeholders until you have proper icons.

## Without Icons:
PWA will show console errors but app will still work.
Just won't be installable until icons are added.
